        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I've rebased on `master` since new `news.txt` caused conflicts. I've also updated the message to reflect the actual implementation (`address` -> `addr`, `is_current` -> `own`).\r\n\r\n*Edit*: Regarding the Windows CI failure: it threw exit code and a bunch of `EOF`s from provider tests. I don't know much about Windows in development (not using), but this looks like a broken Windows runner or missing DLLs rather than an issue with Lua code. Could anyone confirm?",
            "created_at": "2026-04-29T23:23:56Z",
